text.section:
An appeal may be taken from:
An order denying an application to compel arbitration made under KRS 417.060;
An order granting an application to stay arbitration made under subsection (2) of KRS 417.060;
An order confirming or denying confirmation of an award;
An order modifying or correcting an award;
An order vacating an award without directing a rehearing; or
A judgment or decree entered pursuant to the provisions of this chapter.
